{"tid":970603,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"評選你最喜愛既Instant Message工具","createTime":"2019-01-06T03:27:09.000Z","updateTime":"2019-01-06T15:36:26.000Z","uid":41523,"like":0,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"a7d959924fb81433b93a198a7361a9a71c508bc6","tid":970603,"uid":41523,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-06T03:27:09.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">1</span><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong>Whatsapp</strong></span><br />\n可謂歷久不衰 抄完Telegram出@功能<br />\n再抄Line既Stickers (部份都關Snapchat事)<br />\n依然係港人既心目中最愛之一<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">2</span><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong>Telegram</strong></span><br />\n最早推出@功能既通訊軟件<br />\n後來出左內置Bot 一度令手機狼人盛極一時<br />\nStickers更加係人人稱頌<br />\n可能係令男友女友們又喜又恨既App<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">3</span><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong>iMsg</strong></span><br />\n只限iPhone用家互相傳訊<br />\nAnimoji功能係X面世後大行其道<br />\nApp內互玩小遊戲亦係朋友之間互動既元素<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">4</span><br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">WeChat</span></strong><br />\n強國全面掘起走在移動支付潮流支端既神作<br />\n愛國者必備 通訊特點欠奉<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">5</span><br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">Snapchat</span></strong><br />\n90後必備 以圖代字 遊戲互動元素<br />\nStory式動態亦成為Whatsapp抄襲元素之一<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">6</span><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong>Facebook Messager</strong></span><br />\nFacebook附帶之傳訊功能<br />\n方便係冇電話號碼情況下既通訊<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">7</span><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong>Instagram</strong></span><br />\n同上 後期加入錄音功能<br />\n亦有Snapchat式以圖代字傳訊<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">8</span><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong>Line</strong></span><br />\n可能係最早推出免費打網絡電話之軟件<br />\nStickers大受歡迎 Line Friends攻陷萬千俊男美女<br />\n後期大量用戶中毒/被Hack令Line一沉不起<br />\nLine Friends黎不得不提Tsumtsum<br />\n<br />\n&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;<br />\n<br />\n原諒我打打下口語白話又變成書面語<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/clown2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">以下開放討論</span>"},{"pid":"ebee0bdf4d4f25e7c69e360f83ed90939be1d378","tid":970603,"uid":41523,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-06T15:36:26.000Z","msg":"負評完都評選下🤯"}]}